#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn15.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. The First Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Pathavīsutta "
msgstr "2. The Earth "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.179, sc1
msgctxt "sn15.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.2:1.2"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. "

msgctxt "sn15.2:1.3"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ. "
msgstr "No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. "

msgctxt "sn15.2:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso imaṃ mahāpathaviṃ kolaṭṭhimattaṃ kolaṭṭhimattaṃ mattikāguḷikaṃ karitvā nikkhipeyya: "
msgstr "Suppose a person was to make the whole earth into clay balls the size of jujube seeds. They’d lay them down, saying: "

msgctxt "sn15.2:1.5"
msgid "‘ayaṃ me pitā, tassa me pitu ayaṃ pitā’ti, apariyādinnāva bhikkhave, tassa purisassa pitupitaro assu, athāyaṃ mahāpathavī parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya. "
msgstr "‘This is my father, this is my grandfather.’ The whole earth would run out before that person’s fathers and grandfathers. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.2:1.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn15.2:1.7"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. "

msgctxt "sn15.2:1.8"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ. "
msgstr "No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. "

msgctxt "sn15.2:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ dīgharattaṃ vo, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ tibbaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ byasanaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ, kaṭasī vaḍḍhitā. "
msgstr "For such a long time you have undergone suffering, agony, and disaster, swelling the cemeteries. "

msgctxt "sn15.2:1.10"
msgid "Yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhave, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ, alaṃ virajjituṃ, alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.2:1.11"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

